{
  "texts": [
    "Nonetheless, the scientists acknowledge several remaining hurdles to overcome before quantum GANs are routinely employed in drug development.",
    "The scarcity of and the need for more sophisticated VQCs are contributing factors.",
    "Overall, the findings of this article are intriguing and show promise for using quantum GANs in the pharmaceutical industry.",
    "However, whether or not this promise may be realized requires more study (Mao et al., 2023).",
    "Another study suggested a GAN based on a transformer for developing antiviral drugs."
  ]
}